data.description: Darling 2+Den villa with 1564 sf under air. PRICED TO SELL! CALL TODAY! Welcome home to Babcock Ranch - America's 1st solar powered town! This floor plan features open concept living with 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, plus den, custom blinds in LR and Master and a 2 car garage. Light and bright interior paint, granite countertops, white cabinetry,  Low HOA which includes landscaping! HUGE extended lanai. Why wait for something to be built, when this villa is ready for you NOW!  Babcock Ranch has public, schools, medical facilities, restaurants, shops, running trails, dog park,.......Green space downtown called Founder's Square where Friday nights have live bands and food trucks, and Sundays have an open air green market.  NOT TO BE MISSED! This villa is move in ready.This material is based upon information which we consider reliable, but because third parties have supplied it, we cannot represent that it is accurate, or complete and it should not be relied upon as such. It is the responsibility of the buyer's agent and/or their client to verify all fees, potential assessments, measurements and representations. Agent/broker not responsible for errors.
